<li>Preference to lighter weight DE</li>
<li>Solid Support and Dev Sub-Community</li>
<li>Must respect <a href=\"http://blog.sidstamm.com/2012/12/what-is-privacy.html\" target=\"_blank\">privacy</a></li>
</ul>
<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The conclusion for me based on those requirements was that Xubuntu was the best candidate for my 30-day challenge although I did consider Kubuntu. But their lack of shipping Firefox as a default was a deal breaker for me even though they still have an equally crisp desktop.</p>
