<li><a href=\"https://github.com/erikvold/addon-pathfinder/blob/master/lib/panic.js\"><code>pathfinder/panic</code></a> a module that can cause a panic!</li>
<li><a href=\"https://github.com/erikvold/addon-pathfinder/blob/master/lib/content/policy.js\"><code>pathfinder/content/policy</code></a> Allows one to reject network requests.</li>
<li><a href=\"https://github.com/erikvold/addon-pathfinder/blob/master/lib/content/permissions.js\"><code>pathfinder/content/permissions</code></a> Allows one to set permissions for content domains.</li>
<li><a href=\"https://github.com/erikvold/addon-pathfinder/blob/master/lib/addon/folder.js\"><code>pathfinder/addon/folder</code></a> Provides a folder in the user’s profile directory that can be used to read and write files or more folders.</li>
<li><a href=\"https://github.com/erikvold/addon-pathfinder/blob/master/lib/scheme/about.js\"><code>pathfinder/scheme/about</code></a> API to create <code>about:what</code> URLs</li>
<li><a href=\"https://github.com/erikvold/addon-pathfinder/blob/master/lib/download.js\"><code>pathfinder/download</code></a> Easy API for downloading files to the HD.</li>
