<li><a href=\"https://github.com/erikvold/addon-pathfinder/blob/master/lib/ui/findbar/suggestion.js\"><code>pathfinder/ui/finderbar/suggestion</code></a> Allows one to add find bar suggestions.</li>
<li><a href=\"https://github.com/erikvold/addon-pathfinder/blob/master/lib/devtools/gcli.js\"><code>pathfinder/devtools/gcli</code></a> Makes it easy to add new gcli commands.</li>
