<p>We are already seeing interesting opportunities <em>especially</em> in emerging markets – from mobile banking for the previously unbanked (e.g. Safaricom's and Vodafone's <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/M-Pesa\">M-Pesa</a>) to market information systems for farmers (using SMS messaging - e.g. Intuit's <a href=\"http://fasal.intuit.com/\">Fasal</a>) and much more.</p>
